ge cost per square foot to build a home. There are a handful of estimating tools out there to determine how much it actually costs to build a house per square foot. However, these tools will only get you so far in the process.","<strong>Contractors</strong><br/>Speak with contractors. Yes, multiple. Speaking to more than one contractor will help in a number of different ways. First, it will give you more than one estimate for average cost per square foot to build a home. Second, it will allow you to see the differences in home building options that are out there. Not all contractors do things the same, and each contractor offers different home styles.","<strong>Know What You Want</strong><br/>Decide what you want before you start the process of estimating the average cost per square foot to build a home. There are a lot of extra costs that people often don&#39;t think about before jumping into the process, and being prepared with the style and size of home you want, among other things, will help when you dive in.","<strong>Keep Your Options Open</strong><br/>Going with the first estimate that you get may set you back in costs if you don&#39;t at least get a second estimate. Keeping your options open when estimating the average cost per square foot to build a home may save you money when you&#39;re ready to build."]},"id":"2b9dc7f8-06a4-4150-8232-7892bda04a65","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_8858","url":"/5-ways-to-estimate-cost-per-square-foot-to-build-a-house","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"kira-terry","url":"/author/kira-terry","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Kira Terry","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"Lg9uFDyvy5KKTDvpstGsja","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-10-20T17:27:01Z","datePublished":"2014-10-20T17:27:01Z","name":"5 Ways to Estimate Cost per Square Foot to Build a House","synopsis":"When you're looking into building a home, there are likel